    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_2ebcc797-33b2-4ffe-aeb3-a06b907311e1" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can download a PDF with all the comments on a student's submission in SpeedGrader. If an assignment is anonymous, the Download Submissions Comments link is not displayed until the assignment is unmuted or assignment grades are posted. </p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-speedgrader" data-step-uuid="7f5e1b4f-db18-48dd-bacd-e214e07d740c">
    <h2 id="open-speedgrader" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open SpeedGrader</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/910/546/original/8876c17f-59bb-462e-8551-5d3e89e9d668.png" srcset="" alt="Open SpeedGrader" height="52" width="156">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_467ece9c-76c0-4689-bbf1-cade756f31c2" class="text-block-content">
    <p><a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-get-to-SpeedGrader-from-an-assignment-quiz-or-graded/ta-p/759" target="_blank">Open SpeedGrader</a> from any assignment, graded discussion, or quiz.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-student-submission" data-step-uuid="3e2813ec-7e17-43f0-95ef-6d2ee291dcf4">
    <h2 id="open-student-submission" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Student Submission</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/910/548/original/b674c8b5-28d6-4517-915a-469b3c0d586a.png" srcset="" alt="Open Student Submission" height="315" width="373">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_40679d26-b4a2-4745-9c4d-f57ea28ffde8" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Use the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-student-list-to-view-student-submissions-in/ta-p/770" target="_blank">student list</a> to locate a student submission.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="download-submission-comments" data-step-uuid="3ef6f7fa-8e98-4365-be05-5733d1fa48d3">
    <h2 id="download-submission-comments" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Download Submission Comments</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/392/367/original/d6a87512-0d0b-4f4f-ae97-a3b830daa6d1.png" srcset="" alt="Download Submission Comments" height="553" width="326">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_c1bb59ed-fdec-4735-946b-934459b0fce6" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Assignment Comments section [1] in the Sidebar, click the <strong>Download Submission Comments</strong> link [2]. The PDF opens in a new tab in your browser.</p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li>If the assignment is supported by Assignment Enhancements, the Assignment Comments section may display as Comments for this Attempt.</li>
<li>If an assignment is anonymous, the Download Submission Comments link will not display until the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-hide-or-post-assignment-grades-in-SpeedGrader/ta-p/1000" target="_blank">assignment grades are posted</a>.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-submission-comments-pdf" data-step-uuid="3fafd977-7ffc-4a76-8715-6a30de692574">
    <h2 id="view-submission-comments-pdf" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Submission Comments PDF</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/392/370/original/df1df27c-7c9f-40d4-b6a5-9a252fbf2a97.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/392/370/medium/df1df27c-7c9f-40d4-b6a5-9a252fbf2a97.png" srcset="" alt="View Submission Comments PDF" height="209" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_238effae-a6a1-419a-8bbf-8823fb6058af" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The PDF file displays information about the assignment including the assignment name, course name, student name, assignment score, and the account where the course resides [1]. Each included comment displays the name of the user who created the comment, the comment, and the date and time of the comment [2].</p>
<p>To download the PDF to your computer, click the <strong>Download</strong> icon [3].</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>To<strong> </strong>print the submission comments, click the <strong>Print</strong> icon [4].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
